### ============================================
### EMPLOYEE ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### 1. List Employees (Paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get Single Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees/698c6c7691f550b7ea37e611
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Create Employee (Permanent)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_code": "EMP-kaingbsdfgu34nly",
  "full_name": "John Doe",
  "department": "Engineering",
  "position": "Senior Developer",
  "employment_type": "permanent",
  "status": "active"
}

### 4. Create Employee (Contract)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_code": "kaingbunlsadfyasdf1201",
  "full_name": "Jane Smith",
  "department": "Marketing",
  "position": "Marketing Manager",
  "employment_type": "contract",
  "contract": {
    "start_date": "2026-01-01",
    "end_date": "2026-12-31",
    "salary_type": "monthly",
    "rate": 5000.00,
    "pay_on_holiday": true,
    "pay_on_weekend": false
  },
  "status": "active"
}

### 5. Update Employee
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees/698c68815a69b291bad62f5a
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "John Doe Updated999",
  "position": "Lead Developer",
  "department": "Engineering"
}

### 6. Create Account for Employee
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees/698c9f1636da45b288fbee3f/create-account
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "kaingbunly@company.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "username": "kaingbunly1202",
  "role": "employee"
}

### 7. Upload Employee Photo
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/uploads/employee/EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="photo"; filename="photo.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/photo.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 8. Soft Delete Employee
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees/EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE/soft-delete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Restore Employee
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees/EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. List Deleted Employees
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees?deleted_only=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ============================================
### LEAVE ENDPOINTS
### ============================================

### 1. List All Leaves
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. List Leaves by Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves?employee_id=EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. List Leaves by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Single Leave
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves/LEAVE_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Submit Leave Request (Employee)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/employee/leaves
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employee_id": "698c6c7691f550b7ea37e611",
  "leave_type": "annual",
  "start_date": "2026-03-01",
  "end_date": "2026-03-05",
  "reason": "Family vacation"
}

### 6. Update Leave Request (Pending Only)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves/698c6c7691f550b7ea37e611
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_date": "2026-03-02",
  "end_date": "2026-03-06",
  "reason": "Updated: Family vacation extended"
}

### 7. Approve Leave (Manager)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/manager/leaves/LEAVE_ID_HERE/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "Approved. Enjoy your vacation!"
}

### 8. Reject Leave (Manager)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/manager/leaves/LEAVE_ID_HERE/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "Sorry, we need you during this period."
}

### 9. Cancel Leave (Employee)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves/LEAVE_ID_HERE/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Soft Delete Leave
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves/LEAVE_ID_HERE/soft-delete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Restore Leave
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves/LEAVE_ID_HERE/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. List Deleted Leaves
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves?deleted_only=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ============================================
### SEARCH & FILTER EXAMPLES
### ============================================

### Search Employees by Name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees?q=john&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Search Leaves by Reason
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves?q=vacation
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter Pending Leaves for Specific Employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/leaves?employee_id=EMPLOYEE_ID_HERE&status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Include Deleted Records
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/hrms/admin/employees?include_deleted=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
